parameters:
Dining Hall Lady: Ah, it's busy! I wonder if there's anyone
who can help me.
Dining Hall Lady: Oh, are you going to help?

Dining Hall Lady: Whenever you have spare time, feel free to
ask if you want to earn some extra money by helping out in
the kitchen.

Dining Hall Lady: That's a great response! It's time for
cooking in the kitchen!

Dining Hall Lady: You've got some skills! Take this, even
though it's not much!

Dining Hall Lady: There might be some mistakes, but please
help again.

Clea: I-I'm here! I heard there's information about a
dragon!

Clea: Please tell me anything, no matter how trivial it may
be!
Cafeteria Lady: Oh my, oh my, what an intense atmosphere.
Thief Nora: Th-This, it's from Mr. Stolge.

Cafeteria Lady: Oh my, oh my, this is definitely mine! So
that means you all are members of the guild, huh?
Clea: Please tell me about the dragon!

Cafeteria Lady: Well, let's see, the dragon is a big
eater...
Cafeteria Lady: She has good taste, and she pays well...
Clea: Is it about the dragon?

Cafeteria Lady: The nickname of the guild leader here is
Agonia, the Gluttonous Dragon.
Cafeteria Lady: What is it? Is it a different topic?
Thief Nora: G-Get a hold of yourself.

Cafeteria Lady: Oh, that's right, please deliver this to the
tool shop!

Cafeteria Lady: If you're feeling down, why don't you eat
something! Celis-chan is also a regular here, you know.

Cafeteria Lady: Haha, that girl is also a big eater, so
she's a splendid dragon!

Cafeteria Lady: Oh, if you guys have some skills, could you
help me out a bit?

Cafeteria Lady: I see, please let me know when you have free
time.

Cafeteria Lady: That's a good response! Now, it's time for
cooking in the kitchen!

Cafeteria Lady: For a first-timer, this is quite something.
It's not much, but please take it.

Cafeteria Lady: Whenever you have free time, if there's a
shortage of cooks, please let me know and earn some pocket
money.

Young Worker: This place is delicious, cheap, and fast! It's
a friend to workers like us.

Cafeteria Staff: Welcome! It's busy as always today, busy,
busy!

Cafeteria Staff: Welcome! It's another busy, busy day with
lots of customers!
Veteran Mercenary: Do you have something you need from me?

Veteran Mercenary: The Adventurer's Guild, huh... A neat and
tidy adventurer like you can't handle rough jobs, huh?

Veteran Mercenary: Dragon Slayer... I admit it, as expected
of the adventurer guild, Ftera.

Cheerful Worker: Cheers to this cheerful day! Cheers to the
Supreme God Sol and the Three Goddesses!

Dishwashing Baeru: Although my dream of being a court chef
has ended, I think this life isn't so bad.

Dishwashing Baeru: If you're okay with it, I would like you
to accept this as a way for me to atone for my sins and
start anew as a chef.

Dishwashing Baeru: I'll go back to basics and show you my
own cooking.
